narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned how to program a study, analyze results, and write up an official Psychology paper.
This semester was a great opportunity to practice research skills, techniques, and experimental design.

Through my Senior Essay I was able to focus in on the research I have been doing in the lab. Through writing my thesis I was able to synthesize my research and analyze it in the broader context of memory and drug research.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The course was organized very well, and I had a lot of guidance from my advisors.
The course was great for gaining practice in research skills and was very highly individualized to meet my needs and research goals.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would recommend doing research in order to fulfill the BS requirement of the psychology major.
I recommend this course to anyone who wants experience in research.
